name: Ex-Tech Plastics EX-ALLOY 200 - REPROCESSED VINYL
description:
Plastics has long been a market leader in reprocessing vinyl sheet used for a variety of high quality thermoformed packaging. From retail packaging to tri-folds to trays to blister and clamshell packaging, brand Ex-Alloy 200 sheet allows you to realize maximum value from your thermoform waste.
Improve your bottom line with our scrap purchase program. Click on the Recycled Plastics section to learn more.
